s Live Coverage by China Media Group\\\" was released in Paris.\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 797, \"end\": 814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China Media Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 832, \"end\": 837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999961240878372, \"rank\": 3.875927242225854e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The document is available in Chinese, English, French and other languages.\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 913, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 886, \"end\": 892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.999277738166682, \"rank\": 0.0007181700835237161, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The report elaborates on the progress CMG has made in the fields of UHD technology, 5G, artificial intelligence and other areas.\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 1043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 953, \"end\": 956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\", \"score\": 0.9968043294040975, \"rank\": 0.003200558507114813, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\"}, {\"begin\": 983, \"end\": 986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultra-high-definition_television\", \"score\": 0.9999088309913137, \"rank\": 9.117726337645392e-05, \"text\": \"UHD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.o